{"tid":81449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學迎春晚會綵排　舞台倒塌砸傷多名學生","createTime":"2017-01-15T10:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T12:33:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5586726c43498379b3ead7e26e3f0181d7b140","tid":81449,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170115/photo/bkncn-20170115114548922-0115_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170115125905\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170115%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170115114548922-0115_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170115125905&h=1d1f3a0c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n農曆新年臨近，不少內地學校都開始準備迎春晚會。河南南陽內鄉縣一所小學前日進行綵排時，舞台背景鐵架疑因大風，突然倒塌，多名年約5、6歲的學生被砸傷。當地官方未有通報事件及傷情，有當地傳媒指至少一名學生腳部骨裂。 <br />\n<br />\n事發前日下午2時許，城板廠鄉前莊小學正在進行迎春晚會綵排。十多名年約5、6歲的學生在台上跳舞，不少家長都在附近看台觀看，豈料正當表演即將結束之際，舞台背景架突然倒塌，連帶拉倒旁邊的大型充氣裝飾。意外後多名學生被送往醫院急救，暫未知實際受傷人數。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170115/photo/bkncn-20170115114548922-0115_05011_001_03b.jpg?20170115125905\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170115%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170115114548922-0115_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20170115125905&h=28c0a3a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c24d6ac9fe81b9d0c14dd9b28419bb8f9d9d73e","tid":81449,"uid":18489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1d078ddf27262e8ac61bbe3546619cb6ccb812","tid":81449,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wSGhB4iw99Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwSGhB4iw99Y&d=zprXbIA%2Fr9l9%2BaN0GqaKwoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=4dae7ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wSGhB4iw99Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A0315Nyw8HE\" data-sr-url=\"https:/